Try reading in the headings and data separately like this
(shown with read.xls from gdata):

library(gdata)
DF <- read.xls("bikes.xls", skip = 3, header = FALSE,
    col.names = names(read.xls("bikes.xls", skip = 1, nrows = 1)))


